---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Medical Disclaimer - HealthCalcHub"
  description="Read the HealthCalcHub medical disclaimer and important limitations for calculator results and health content."
>
  <section class="section-shell brand-frame soft-grid overflow-hidden p-8 sm:p-10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <span class="eyebrow">Medical Disclaimer</span>
        <span class="wellness-chip">Important before using the site</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="heading-display mt-5">HealthCalcHub is educational, not medical advice.</h1>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg leading-8 text-ink/74">
        The calculators, articles, and explanations on HealthCalcHub are for general informational use only. They are not a diagnosis, treatment plan, or substitute for professional care.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-10 space-y-5">
    <div class="section-shell brand-frame p-6 sm:p-8">
      <h2 class="section-title">What this means in practice</h2>
      <div class="mt-5 space-y-4 text-base leading-8 text-ink/75">
        <p>Calculator outputs are estimates based on the information you enter and the formulas used on the page.</p>
        <p>Those estimates may not reflect your full medical history, medications, training background, pregnancy status, or any condition that changes how a number should be interpreted.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-shell brand-frame p-6 sm:p-8">
      <h2 class="section-title">When to speak with a professional</h2>
      <div class="mt-5 space-y-4 text-base leading-8 text-ink/75">
        <p>If you are making a decision about weight change, pregnancy, nutrition, sleep, alcohol safety, blood pressure, heart rate, or any other health concern, it is best to use these tools as a starting point and confirm next steps with a qualified healthcare professional.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-shell brand-frame p-6 sm:p-8">
      <h2 class="section-title">Emergency situations</h2>
      <div class="mt-5 space-y-4 text-base leading-8 text-ink/75">
        <p>Do not use this website for emergencies. If you think you may be experiencing a medical emergency, contact your local emergency services right away.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
